ED_Title: Provisional programme of work and timetable of the First Committee for 2024
ED_DecisionText: At its 42nd plenary meeting, on 4 December 2023, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the First Committee,  (Footnote: A/78/416, para. 5.) approved the provisional programme of work and timetable of the Committee for 2024, as set out in the annex to the report of the Committee.  (Footnote: A/78/416.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
